  <header>
    <h1 id="title">Baseline</h1>
    <h2>Holistic journal that maps the structure of your life, revealing how your past, present, and future connect. It helps you see time and key metrics clearly so you can focus on what truly matters.</h2>
  </header>
  <section>
    <h2>Key idea</h2>
    <p>
      I’m building a universal self-design system that integrates <a href="/ld" class="link">the personal growth practices I use</a> intoan AI-powered journal. I've been journaling every day since April 2015, and it’s the single practice that has impacted my life the most.
    </p>
    <p>There are many other practices I’ve tested on myself over the past ten years. The problem is, they’re all scattered across different apps, so there’s no way to see the full history or long-term progress.</p>
    <p>Holistic journal connects your past and future through the present moment; blending reflection, self-regulation, and productivity. It maps the structure of your life and helps you write the story you’ll want to remember. It captures your thoughts, emotions, goals, tasks, events, meetings, habits, and key metrics, training your personal assistant with this data.</p>
    <p>It brings you back to the present moment through regular writing, weaving each moment into the larger flow of your life.</p>
  </section>
